struct.exostring:
This dialogue is launched by the player crossing a trigger in 22aa, halfway between the Ebon Hawk and Eli Gand
If Zaalbar ISN'T in the party, the dialogue fires ONCE for some other party member to say something. If Zaalbar is in the party later and croses the trigger, but the plot has not been completed, then this dialogue would launch again for him and him only (this would happen if the player left the Ebon Hawk, explored a bit of Kashyyyk but DID NOT talk to Chuundar, then returned to the ship and picked up Zaalbar)
